    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok so it sounds like the escrow agent is basically just sitting on all this cash waiting for something to happen. feels a bit weird that a random third party just holds onto a big chunk of my money like that. is there any risk of them just... not letting it go if there's a dispute?",
